#: ../../learn.rst:61
msgid "Each time you login into **Kolibri**, the first thing you will see is the **Learn** page. Here you will find learning topics and materials related to what you were doing the last time you used Kolibri, or those recommended by your teachers and coaches (not visible if you are browsing as a guest)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../learn.rst:64
msgid "Recommended"
msgstr ""

#: ../../learn.rst:66
msgid "In the **Recommended** tab you can see various sections:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../learn.rst:68
msgid "**Most popular** displays the most frequently used materials in your school or facility."
msgstr ""

#: ../../learn.rst:69
msgid "**Next steps** displays suggestions according to  topics and materials you previously visited."
msgstr ""

#: ../../learn.rst:70
msgid "**Resume** displays activities that you started but havenâ€™t finished yet."
msgstr ""

#: ../../learn.rst:71
msgid "**Featured in...** displays a preview of activities for each content channel you have access on Kolibri."
msgstr ""

